  %ol{:style => "font-weight: normal"}
    %li Any individual, group or organization, whether affiliated with UBC or not, may apply to enter their blog, website or other media in this contest. The contest administrators plan to require content to be substantially of interest to members of the UBC AMS community.

    %li
      Awards are calculated daily and reported at
      = link_to("votermedia.org/ubc/horserace", "/ubc/horserace") + ","
